        <mxCell id="ZTHXAd76exHzAeLix3zn-58" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="5. If the combat is melee, this halts the target and forces them into Attack state as well. they may start attacking, if they have CAttacker." vertex="1">
