        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZTHXAd76exHzAeLix3zn-63" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="6. Run the FX and move_tween for the attacker, and roll the Combat formula" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="120" x="1160" y="1450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZTHXAd76exHzAeLix3zn-64" parent="1" style="shape=process;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;" value="Chance to Hit: max(Offense - Defense, &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(127, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;MIN_HIT_CHANCE&lt;/font&gt;[1]&lt;br&gt;Chance to Critical Hit: (Offense-Defense) %100&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Offense = Power + &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(127, 0, 255);&quot;&gt;BASE_HIT_CHANCE&lt;/font&gt;[50]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Defense = Defense &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(103, 171, 159);&quot;&gt;* getDamageMatrixBonus()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(103, 171, 159);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Roll a d100. If under Chance to Hit, deal a Wound. If under Chance to Critical Hit, deal 2 Wounds.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="420" x="1330" y="1430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZTHXAd76exHzAeLix3zn-66" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="7. if a hit happens, play the hitflash on the target" vertex="1">
